Package: msxtractor
Type: Package
Title: Simple XIC and MS2 Extraction and Plotting from mzML/mzXML Files
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: person(given = "Amir", family = "Sakhteman", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "amir@example.com")
Description: Small helper functions for extracting extracted ion chromatograms (XICs) from MS1 data, extracting MS2 spectra matching a target precursor m/z, and plotting XIC and MS2 spectra from mzML or mzXML files using MSnbase and ggplot2.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports:
    MSnbase,
    ggplot2
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
